# Add columns with values to pivot tables

1. Additional tables to pivot table
2. Right click table icon to Add Measure
3. Enter Dax formula below (replacing "column_name"):

    =CONCATENATEX(Values(Table1[column_name]), Table1[column_name], ",")


# Add columns with no values to pivot tables. This is used when additoinal columns are needed to align vertical data i.e. forms

1. Additional tables to pivot table
2. Right click table icon to Add Measure
3. Enter Dax formula below (replacing "column_name"):

    =""